      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It sounds like you're experiencing a profound sense of disconnection and disorientation. Feeling like you've lost your sense of identity and purpose can be a really difficult and isolating experience. It's like you're saying goodbye to the person you used to be and don't know who you are anymore. It's not uncommon for people to go through periods like this, though - sometimes, we just need to give ourselves space and time to rediscover who we are and what brings us meaning.",
      "source": "target",
